org.sbfc.converter.sbml2graphml
Class Sbml2Graphml

java.lang.Object
  org.sbfc.converter.sbml2graphml.Sbml2Graphml

public class Sbml2Graphml
extends Object

Class enabling the conversion to a SBML model file to a GraphML file. For the moment only the basic structure of GraphML is implemented, but the idea is to have also additional comments in the file for others purposes. More details about GraphML, see the spec at http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/specification/dtd.html#top

Author:
jalowcki
